snippet.title: WildWood C64 Chase Stage Preview
snippet.description:
A preview of one of the short chase stages between platforming levels from the game WildWood. Find out more at www.wildwoodgame.co.uk

Currently in development for the Commodore 64.

Code: Kodiak (https://kodiak64.com/)
Music: NM156
Graphics and Design: Hend   (You can support my work here  https://ko-fi.com/hendart )
